In Sidereus Nuncius  (Favaro, 1892, 3:81 ) Galileo stated that he had reached this conclusion on January 11.  Drake (1978, p.152), however, after studying unpublished manuscript records of Galileo's observations, concluded that he did not do so until January 15.↩
